org.springframework.integration.channel

Interface ExecutorChannelInterceptorAware

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ChannelInterceptorAware
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractExecutorChannel, AbstractPollableChannel, ExecutorChannel, PollableAmqpChannel, PollableJmsChannel, PriorityChannel, PublishSubscribeChannel, QueueChannel, RendezvousChannel

    public interface ExecutorChannelInterceptorAware
extends ChannelInterceptorAware
    The ChannelInterceptorAware extension for the cases when the ExecutorChannelInterceptors may have reason (e.g. ExecutorChannel or QueueChannel) and the implementors require to know if they should make the ExecutorChannelInterceptor or not.
    Since:
    4.2
    Author:
    Artem Bilan
